title: Rush Rover v1.0
description: Rush Rover is a 2D top-down shooter game. Compared to other similar games of the genre, the shooting experience is closer to traditional shoot'em up games. It includes random map generation, unique weapons, lots of different enemies, exciting boss battles and a dynamic chiptune soundtrack. In the universe of Rush Over, intelligent robots and mining exploration have spread over every known galaxy.
